name: Shopper Cub Holiday Dazzle
description:
The north pole collection coordinates with the snow day patterns to give you expanded options and a really cute twist. Bags and gable box are made with recycled kraft paper and the multi colored design lets you mix and match tissue paper and ribbon for a look that is uniquely yours.

Orders must be placed by August 17th and packaging will be shipped October 31st.

name: Shopper Cub Classic Christmas
description:
Holiday plaid mixed with the artwork of a Thomas Nash Santa these bags make a vintage addition to your holiday packaging.

These recycled kraft bags have a red, green and white print that you can match with other bags, boxes and ribbon or tissue paper.

Orders must be placed by August 17th and packaging will be shipped October 31st.
